        "Description": "Good morning 47,\r\ryour targets are two Italian influencers that within a year made a fortune up to 1 M Euros. They are promoting their cooking brand all over the internet with special recepies that are apperently &quot;invented by them&quot;. One of your target is a face of the brand that also works like a cook while the other is a reporter and undercover agent that seeks for unique recepies.\rMr. Bronzo can be killed in any way, but Mr. &quot;Fabio&quot; needs to face an accident.\r\rGood luck",
